{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "一行人在采掘场深处发现了\\n古代文明的魔导兵器。揭露谢斯秘密的王子\\n被迫在死或听命于她之间做出抉择。\\n因无法赞同谢斯强迫民众牺牲的做法，\\n王子选择了迎战魔导兵器。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120048_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这是……看起来像是\\n古代纪念碑之类的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "卢卡，等一下！别轻易靠近！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120048_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "入侵者，发现。\\n攻击，开始。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哇！这家伙搞什么！？\\n居然发动攻击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这、这家伙到底是什么啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "这难道是，魔导兵器……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "魔导兵器！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "古代大战时使用过的没有心灵的士兵、\\n没有灵魂的魔兽。据说绝大部分\\n都已经被破坏，消失了才对……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里不是远古材料的采掘场吗？\\n怎么会出现那种危险的东西？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "这里是古代的遗迹，\\n所以才会有远古材料产出……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "朱庇特",
            "context": "难道说那位公主在挖掘的\\n不光是宝藏吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "恐怕是的……\\n她也许想同时发掘\\n远古材料和魔导兵器吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "如今局势动荡，\\n想储备武力也情有可原……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "我可不喜欢。\\n它给我一种不祥的预感。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "朱庇特",
            "context": "的确，毕竟狄涅尔帝国曾经使用过。\\n我们身为龙也觉得不舒服。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "狄涅尔帝国的兵器……\\n谢斯姐姐想用这些东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "被你们发现了呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "谢斯姐姐！\\n这里……那个魔导兵器究竟是！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "既然被发现了，\\n就没有必要再隐瞒了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02",
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "那是克里米纳巨像。\\n是我用来统治大陆的决战兵器！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "有了它的力量，就可以把\\n勾结帝国的那些家伙全都大卸八块，\\n把他们住的地方都化作焦土！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "什么！？大卸八块！？化作焦土！？\\n没必要做到那种地步吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "即使在帝国内部，\\n也有许多人是不得已才臣服于帝国。\\n你连那些人也不打算放过吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "那又怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01",
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "卑贱之人只需要考虑\\n如何为我效劳就够了。\\n不服从我的家伙没有活着的价值。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "怎、怎么这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "装模作样地说了那么多漂亮话，\\n结果那才是你真正的想法吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "终于露出狐狸尾巴了吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，什么狐狸尾巴……\\n淑女善变，捉摸不透而已。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "怎么会有这种人。欺骗我们，\\n还在地下暗中策划着这种阴谋……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "本来我可不会让\\n知晓这些秘密的人活下去。不过……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，根据你的选择，\\n倒是也可以放过你们哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "如果你愿意成为我的部下。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "部下……\\n要我听命于你，跟帝国战斗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "没错！只要你愿意帮助我当上女王，\\n我就放你们一马。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "快做决断。让我们\\n还像小时候那样亲密无间吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "姐姐，我做不到……\\n我不能听命于\\n强迫无辜民众牺牲的你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "没错！\\n不听你的话就会被攻击，\\n那和帝国有什么两样！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，你是说我是坏人吗？\\n你们听好了，\\n光靠宣扬理想可没法统治国家哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也许的确如此……\\n但是，不谈理想的统治\\n真的能让人们获得幸福吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我的理想是建立所有人都能\\n快乐生活的国家。为了实现它，\\n姐姐的野心就由我来粉碎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，真遗憾。没想到你\\n竟然是个如此顽固的死脑筋。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "那好吧。\\n既然你不愿意听命于我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "就先让你们统统化成灰！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "克里米纳巨像！\\n动手吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120048_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "克里米纳巨像",
            "context": "入侵者，清除。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "率领遗迹里的魔兽，\\n消灭所有入侵者！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "别了，尤蒂尔、利弗。\\n虽然很伤心，但这也是\\n想要君临天下之人的宿命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "喂！站住！可恶，\\n一旦遗迹里的大批魔兽聚集起来，\\n逼近这里的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120107_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帕蒂亚",
            "context": "怎么办，团长！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_1040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "要想从这里脱身\\n可不是件易事。殿下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0071",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "上吧，利弗。\\n不能让姐姐为所欲为。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0072",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "只要打倒那个魔导兵器，\\n香榭利亚的战斗力应该也会下降。\\n让它见识一下我们团结起来的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_09_08_0073",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}